title: Can music make you sick? With Dr George Musgrave
description:
In this episode, Dr George Musgrave reads chapter one of his book with Sally Anne Gross entitled 'Can Music make you sick; measuring the price of musical ambition'

You can follow George on Twitter - @DrGMusgrave

Chapter two will be coming soon!
